Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:50.15,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在半夜裡睜開眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:53.18,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}狂気 愛 飲み干す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:53.18,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}把愛與瘋狂喝光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:56.53,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}おいでこの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:56.53,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}過來 到我的懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:59.65,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「あっちの闇は苦いぞ」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:59.65,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「那邊的黑暗是苦澀的」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:05.60,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君の惑い 揺らめく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:05.60,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你在迷惘 在動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:09.19,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて永遠になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:09.19,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}最終將永遠無法解脫
